original_title: Jasperina de Jong: Jasperina's Grote Ego-trip
overview: This show is a TV adaptation of Jasperina de Jongs second theater show. The show contains songs about abortion, about revolving flowers, about a man born with inexplicable suicidal tendencies, about the objectification of women and many more.
title: Jasperina de Jong: Jasperina's Grote Ego-trip
